{"tid":2297213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【再有三名旺角魚革義士判囚兩至三年】","createTime":"2020-11-23T06:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T17:17:07.000Z","uid":77536,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12269eda4fda031d3e682834b36f304cff91ac21","tid":2297213,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"2016年初一旺角騷亂發生至今雖近五年，但港共政權仍對當日的被捕者窮追猛打。再有三名義士被告暴動或縱火等罪成，今日分別被判囚27至36個月。<br />\n <br />\n中共與港共政權全方位打壓港人，無人能獨善其身。身陷黑獄的義人需要大家繼續關注，讓他們知道自己的付出並沒有被遺忘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1965117443775378/posts/2934815973472182/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1965117443775378%2Fposts%2F2934815973472182%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=4195df38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1965117443775378/posts/2934815973472182/</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/sparkalliancehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsparkalliancehk&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=338cb668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sparkalliancehk</a>"},{"pid":"0649a9dfde7cf3d4a01063477909a98f7712d445","tid":2297213,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />清算一直進行緊"},{"pid":"820a1bf176335722059b36cb857ed5142ccd4374","tid":2297213,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946b8775d7a359863be033bf3f6cb08a740506e2","tid":2297213,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl